'''伦敦'''（{{lang-en|London}}；{{IPAc-en|audio=En-uk-London.ogg|ˈ|l|ʌ|n|d|ən}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/london?showCookiePolicy=true|title=London|accessdate=2014-09-23|publisher=Collins Dictionary|date=n.d.|archive-date=2020-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200816152112/https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/london?showCookiePolicy=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是[[英国|英国]]首都，也是英國最大都市<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/uk.html|title=The World Factbook|date=2014-02-01|work=[[Central_Intelligence_Agency|Central Intelligence Agency]]|accessdate=2014-02-23|archive-date=2019-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107065049/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/uk.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、以及其[[英國的構成國|構成國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]]的首府。位于[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]流域，于公元50年由[[古罗马|罗马人]]建立，取名为[[伦蒂尼恩|伦蒂尼恩]]，在此后两个世纪内为这一地区最重要的定居点之一<ref name=london_001>{{cite web |url=http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Permanent/RomanLondon.htm |date=n.d. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622181424/http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Permanent/RomanLondon.htm |title=Roman London |publisher=[[Museum_of_London|Museum of London]] |archivedate=2008-06-22 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2009-06-30 }}</ref>。伦敦的历史核心区——[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]仍旧维持其[[中世纪|中世纪]]的界限，面积{{convert|1.12|sqmi}}，2019年人口为898.2萬，为全英格兰最大的[[英国城市地位|城市]]。自19世纪起，“伦敦”一称亦用于指稱围绕这一核心区开发的周围地带<ref name="mills_140">{{Harvnb|Mills|2001|p=140}}</ref>。这一[[组合城市|城区集合]]自1965年起构成[[大倫敦|大倫敦]][[英格蘭都會郡和非都會郡|行政区]]，由32個[[倫敦自治市鎮|倫敦自治市]]加上倫敦市組成<ref name="region">{{cite web |url=http://www.gos.gov.uk/gol/factgol/London/?a=42496 |title=Government Offices for the English Regions, Fact Files: London |publisher=Office for National Statistics |accessdate=2008-05-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080124102915/http://www.gos.gov.uk/gol/factgol/London/?a=42496 |archivedate=2008-01-24 }}</ref><ref name="elcock">{{Cite book |last= Elcock |first=Howard |title=Local Government: Policy and Management in Local Authorities |url= https://archive.org/details/localgovernmentp0000elco |publisher=Routledge |location= London |year=1994 |isbn=978-0-415-10167-7|page=368|ref=harv}}</ref>，由[[伦敦市长_(大伦敦)|伦敦市长]]及[[伦敦议会|伦敦议会]]管辖。<ref name="politics_uk">{{Cite book |last=Jones |first=Bill |coauthors=Kavanagh, Dennis; Moran, Michael; Norton, Philip |title=Politics UK |url=https://archive.org/details/politicsuk0000unse |publisher=Pearson Education |year=2007 |isbn=978-1-4058-2411-8 |page=[https://archive.org/details/politicsuk0000unse/page/868 868] |ref=harv |location=Harlow}}</ref><ref group="注">伦敦市长与[[伦敦市市长|伦敦市市长]]非同一概念；后者为[[伦敦市法团|伦敦市法团]]领导者，即伦敦城的管辖者。</ref>

伦敦亦是一个[[全球城市|全球城市]]<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/shortcuts/2013/mar/10/london-capital-of-world-divorce-breakfast |title= London: the everything capital of the world |work= [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |author= Adewunmi, Bim |date= 2013-03-10 |location= London |accessdate= 2015-05-21 |archive-date= 2013-03-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130313042156/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/shortcuts/2013/mar/10/london-capital-of-world-divorce-breakfast |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://moreintelligentlife.co.uk/content/ideas/john-parker/what-capital-world?page=full |title=What's The Capital Of The World? |publisher=More Intelligent Life |accessdate=2013-07-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922132807/http://moreintelligentlife.co.uk/content/ideas/john-parker/what-capital-world?page=full |archivedate=2013-09-22 }}</ref>，名列紐倫港世界三大國際都會之一。<ref>[http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1704398,00.html A Tale Of Three Cities] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1704398,00.html |date=20130826061224 }}，《時代雜誌》， 2008年1月17日</ref>在文艺、商业、教育、娱乐、时尚、金融、健康、媒体、专业服务、研究与发展、旅游和交通方面都具有显著的地位<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.forbes.com/pictures/edgl45ghmd/no-1-london |title= The World's Most Influential Cities 2014 |accessdate= 2015-03-02 |publisher= Forbes |archive-date= 2020-08-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200816152147/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/edgl45ghmd/no-1-london/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.mori-m-foundation.or.jp/gpci/index_e.html |title= Global Power City Index 2014 |accessdate= 2015-03-02 |publisher= Institute for Urban Strategies – The Mori Memorial Foundation |archive-date= 2020-12-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201207054751/http://www.mori-m-foundation.or.jp/gpci/index_e.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/london-is-the-most-desirable-city-in-the-world-to-work-in-study-finds-9779868.html |title= London is 'the most desirable city in the world to work in', study finds |accessdate= 2015-03-02 |publisher= The Independent |archive-date= 2020-09-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200916080252/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/london-is-the-most-desirable-city-in-the-world-to-work-in-study-finds-9779868.html |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.londonandpartners.com/media-centre/press-releases/2014/20141218london-leads-the-uk-for-worldclass-research |title= London leads the UK for world-class research |accessdate= 2015-03-02 |publisher= London & Partners |archive-date= 2019-04-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190401181841/https://www.londonandpartners.com/media-centre/press-releases/2014/20141218london-leads-the-uk-for-worldclass-research |dead-url= no }}</ref>，同时还是全球主要[[国际金融中心|金融中心]]之一<ref name="Mastercard">{{cite web |url= http://www.mastercard.com/us/company/en/insights/pdfs/2008/MCWW_WCoC-Report_2008.pdf |title= Worldwide Centres of Commerce Index 2008 |publisher= Mastercard |accessdate= 2015-05-21 |archive-date= 2008-06-24 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20080624211344/http://www.mastercard.com/us/company/en/insights/pdfs/2008/MCWW_WCoC-Report_2008.pdf |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Global Financial Centres 10">{{cite web |url=http://zyen.com/PDF/GFCI%2010.pdf |title=Global Financial Centres 9 |publisher=[[Z/Yen|Z/Yen]] |year=2011 |access-date=2015-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008222617/http://zyen.com/PDF/GFCI%2010.pdf |archive-date=2011-10-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="forbes.com">{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2008/07/15/economic-growth-gdp-biz-cx_jz_0715powercities.html |title=World's Most Economically Powerful Cities |work=Forbes |location=New York |date=2008-07-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0LhcwS?url=http://www.forbes.com/2008/07/15/economic-growth-gdp-biz-cx_jz_0715powercities.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref>，根据计算，为全球[[世界城市国内生产总值列表|国内生产总值第六大的都市区]]<ref group="注">由于对城市界限的定义、人口的规模、汇率的变化及产出的计算方式不同，城市都市区GDP的排名可能有一定的差别。伦敦和[[巴黎|巴黎]]在总经济产出方面大致规模相近，由此第三方的不同估计对于第五和第六大城市GDP的排列可能不同。麦肯锡全球研究所2012年的报告估计伦敦全市2010年的GDP为US$7,518亿，巴黎则为$7,642亿，由此两市分别为第六和第五。普华永道2009年11月发布的报告称，根据购买力平价计算，2008年伦敦的GDP为US$5,650亿，巴黎则为US$5,640亿，分别为第五和第六。麦肯锡的研究中伦敦人口为1,490万，巴黎则为1,180万，而普华永道的研究中伦敦人口为859万，巴黎992万</ref><ref name=forpolgdp>{{cite news |url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2012/08/13/the_most_dynamic_cities_of_2025 |title=The Most Dynamic Cities of 2025 |accessdate=2012-09-28 |work=Foreign Policy |date=September–October 2012 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CI3k4DBe?url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2012/08/13/the_most_dynamic_cities_of_2025 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Global city GDP rankings 2008-2025">{{cite web |url=http://www.ukmediacentre.pwc.com/Media-Library/Global-city-GDP-rankings-2008-2025-61a.aspx |title=Global city GDP rankings 2008–2025 |publisher=PricewaterhouseCoopers |accessdate=2010-11-16 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0M2ast?url=http://www.ukmediacentre.pwc.com/Media-Library/Global-city-GDP-rankings-2008-2025-61a.aspx |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。伦敦亦是全球文化首都之一<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/london-capital-of-the-world-766661.html |location=London |work=The Independent |first=Simon |last=Calder |date=2007-12-22 |title=London, capital of the world |accessdate=2015-05-21 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118074722/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/london-capital-of-the-world-766661.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/news/article-23389580-london-is-the-world-capital-of-the-21st-century-says-new-york.do |author=Teodorczuk, Tom |title=London is the world capital of the 21st century ... says New York |work=London Evening Standard |date=2007-03-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091125151618/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/news/article-23389580-london-is-the-world-capital-of-the-21st-century-says-new-york.do |archivedate=2009-11-25 |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www2.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2008/culturecapital.aspx |title=London is world capital of culture says LSE expert |publisher=London School of Economics |date=2008-03-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111118132607/http://www2.lse.ac.uk/newsAndMedia/news/archives/2008/culturecapital.aspx |archivedate=2011-11-18 |access-date=2015-05-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/get-involved/consultations/current-consultations/cultural-strategy |title=Cultural Strategy |publisher=Greater London Authority |date=2010-09-06 |accessdate=2012-02-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209210256/http://www.london.gov.uk/get-involved/consultations/current-consultations/cultural-strategy |archivedate=2012-02-09 }}</ref>，还是全球国际访客数量最多的城市<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/london-tops-ranking-of-destination-cities-2291794.html |title= London tops ranking of destination cities |accessdate= 2012-06-12 |newspaper= The Independent |location= London |date= 2011-06-01 |archive-date= 2011-06-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110603143149/http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/news-and-advice/london-tops-ranking-of-destination-cities-2291794.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>，根据客流量计算则拥有[[全球城市机场系统列表|全球最为繁忙的城市机场系统]]<ref name=capa1>{{cite web |url= http://www.centreforaviation.com/analysis/beijing-to-overtake-london-as-worlds-largest-aviation-hub-massive-new-airport-planned-58776 |title= Beijing to overtake london as world's largest aviation hub |accessdate= 2012-06-12 |publisher= Centre for Aviation |archive-date= 2012-03-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120327061035/http://www.centreforaviation.com/analysis/beijing-to-overtake-london-as-worlds-largest-aviation-hub-massive-new-airport-planned-58776 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。倫敦是全球領先投資地<ref>{{cite web |title=Global Cities Investment Monitor 2016 |url=http://www.agefi.fr/sites/agefi.fr/files/fichiers/2016/07/gpia-kpmg-gcim_2016.pdf |website=www.agefi.fr |accessdate=2019-04-25 |archive-date=2016-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020012814/http://www.agefi.fr/sites/agefi.fr/files/fichiers/2016/07/gpia-kpmg-gcim_2016.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，吸引很多國際零售商來投資<ref>{{cite web |author1=Bourke, Joanna |title=London retains title as world's most international shopping destination |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/london-retains-title-as-worlds-most-international-shopping-destination-10258033.html |website=standard.co.uk |publisher=London Evening Standard. |accessdate=2019-04-25 |archive-date=2020-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206220436/https://www.standard.co.uk/business/business-news/london-retains-title-as-worlds-most-international-shopping-destination-10258033.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，個人凈資產值高於其它城市<ref>{{cite web |title=The Wealth Report 2015 |url=http://www.knightfrank.com/research/the-wealth-report-2015-2716.aspx |publisher=Knight Frank. |accessdate=2019-04-25 |archive-date=2016-05-17 |archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160517203239/http://www.knightfrank.com/research/the-wealth-report-2015-2716.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伦敦拥有43所大学，其高等教育机构密集度在全欧洲最高<ref name="london2">{{cite press release |date=2008-08-20 |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/media/press_releases_mayoral/number-international-students-london-continues-grow |title=Number of international students in London continues to grow |publisher=Greater London Authority |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0OvJq8?url=http://www.london.gov.uk/media/press_releases_mayoral/number-international-students-london-continues-grow |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes |access-date=2015-05-21 }}</ref>。[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2012年]]，伦敦成为史上首座三次举办现代[[夏季奥林匹克运动会|夏季奥林匹克运动会]]的城市。<ref name=IOC>{{cite web |url=http://www.olympic.org/media?calendartab=1&articleid=52922 |title=IOC elects London as the Host City of the Games of the XXX Olympiad in 2012 |date=2005-07-06 |publisher=[[International_Olympic_Committee|International Olympic Committee]] |accessdate=2006-06-03 |archive-date=2011-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111017100349/http://www.olympic.org/media?calendartab=1&articleid=52922 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

伦敦的人口和文化十分多样，在大伦敦地区内使用的语言就超过300种<ref name=london_006>{{cite web |url=http://www.cilt.org.uk/faqs/langspoken.htm |title=Languages spoken in the UK population |publisher=National Centre for Language |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0PFX8H?url=http://www.cilt.org.uk/faqs/langspoken.htm |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。这一区域2015年的官方统计人口为8,673,713<ref name=ons-pop-estimates/>，人口占全英国的12.5%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://data.london.gov.uk/datastore/applications/focus-london-population-and-migration |title=Focus on London – Population and Migration | London DataStore |publisher=Greater London Authority |accessdate=2012-02-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101016225915/http://data.london.gov.uk/datastore/applications/focus-london-population-and-migration |archivedate=2010-10-16 }}</ref>。[[大伦敦都会区|伦敦的城市区]]为[[欧盟最大城市区列表|欧盟第二大]]，根据2011年普查其人口达到9,787,426，仅次于[[巴黎|巴黎]]<ref name="urbanpopulation">{{cite web| url=http://www.nomisweb.co.uk/articles/747.aspx| title=2011 Census – Built-up areas| publisher=[[Office_for_National_Statistics|ONS]]| accessdate=2013-06-29| archive-date=2013-09-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921045319/http://www.nomisweb.co.uk/articles/747.aspx| dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[倫敦通勤帶|其都市区]]为[[欧盟都市区列表|欧洲最大]]，人口达13,614,409{{refn|根据[[欧洲统计局|欧洲统计局]]数据，伦敦的大城市区（[[组合城市|组合城市]]及高人口区域）为欧洲最大。基于城区行政界限内的[[欧盟城市人口列表|人口排名]]将伦敦排在第一位。然而法国阿维尼翁大学则称，当整个都市区及其内陆地区计算在内时，巴黎为最大城市。|group=注}}<ref name="appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu show">{{cite web |url= http://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=met_pjanaggr3&lang=en |title= Metropolitan Area Populations |publisher= Eurostat |date= 2012-08-30 |accessdate= 2013-05-04 |archive-date= 2016-08-22 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160822103143/http://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=met_pjanaggr3&lang=en |dead-url= no }}</ref>，而[[大伦敦政府|大伦敦政府]]则称伦敦都市区的总人口为2,100万<ref>[http://www.london.gov.uk/thelondonplan/introduction/positioning.jsp The London Plan – Introduction – Positioning London] {{Wayback|url=http://www.london.gov.uk/thelondonplan/introduction/positioning.jsp |date=20140407025007 }}. Greater London Authority. Retrieved 12 July 2013.</ref>。1831年—1925年间，伦敦为世界最大的城市。<ref name=london_030>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/i-m/london4.html |title=London: The greatest city |publisher=Channel 4 |accessdate=2008-10-12 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0g3KOn?url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/i-m/london4.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

有四项[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]位于伦敦，分别为：[[伦敦塔|伦敦塔]]；[[邱园|邱园]]；[[威斯敏斯特宫|威斯敏斯特宫]]、[[威斯敏斯特教堂|威斯敏斯特教堂]]和[[威斯敏斯特圣玛格丽特教堂|圣玛格丽特教堂]]；以及[[格林尼治|格林尼治]]历史区（其中的[[格林尼治皇家天文台|皇家天文台]]为[[本初子午线|本初子午线]]、0°[[经度|经线]]和[[格林尼治标准时间|格林尼治标准时间]]所经之地）<ref name=london_005>{{cite web |url=http://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/gb |title=Lists: United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland |publisher=[[UNESCO|UNESCO]] |accessdate=2008-11-26 |archive-date=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007220215/http://whc.unesco.org/en/statesparties/gb/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他著名景点包括[[白金汉宫|白金汉宫]]、[[伦敦眼|伦敦眼]]、[[皮卡迪利圆环|皮卡迪利圆环]]、[[圣保罗座堂|圣保罗座堂]]、[[伦敦塔桥|伦敦塔桥]]、[[特拉法加广场|特拉法加广场]]和[[碎片大厦|碎片大厦]]。伦敦亦是诸多博物馆、画廊、图书馆、体育运动及其他文化机构的所在地，包括[[大英博物馆|大英博物馆]]、[[國家美術館_(倫敦)|国家美术馆]]、[[泰特现代艺术馆|泰特现代艺术馆]]、[[大英图书馆|大英图书馆]]以及40家[[西区剧院|西区剧院]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.whatsonstage.com/index.php?pg=207&story=E8821201275286&title=West+End+Must+Innovate+to+Renovate%2C+Says+Report |title=West End Must Innovate to Renovate, Says Report |accessdate=2010-11-15 |work=What's On Stage |date=2008-01-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0S4x3M?url=http://www.whatsonstage.com/index.php?pg=207 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |location=London |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[伦敦地铁|伦敦地铁]]是全球最古老的地下铁路网络。<ref name=Metro150>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-20641351 |title=Oyster card celebrates 150th Tube anniversary |work=BBC News |date=2012-12-10 |accessdate=2013-01-10 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123182556/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-20641351 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="railwaygazette.com">{{cite news |url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/shanghai-now-the-worlds-longest-metro.html |title=Shanghai now the world's longest metro |date=2010-05-04 |work=[[Railway_Gazette_International|Railway Gazette International]] |accessdate=2010-05-04 |location=London |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0Tj3yO?url=http://www.railwaygazette.com/news/single-view/view/10/shanghai-now-the-worlds-longest-metro.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>

== 历史 ==
{{Main|伦敦历史}}

===名称===
{{main|伦敦名称由来}}
[[File:London_Thames_Sunset_panorama_-_Feb_2008.jpg|thumb]]]]
{{le|伦敦名称由来|Etymology of London|伦敦名称的由来}}不详<ref name="mills_139">{{Harvnb|Mills|2001|p=139}}</ref>。这一名称在2世纪即已存在，在公元约121年记载为[[伦蒂尼恩|伦蒂尼恩]]（{{lang|la|Londinium}}），证明其来源有[[罗马-不列颠文化|罗马-不列颠]]背景<ref name="mills_139"/>。[[蒙茅斯的杰弗里|蒙茅斯的杰弗里]]在其作品《[[不列颠诸王史|不列颠诸王史]]》中最先试图阐释这一名称，但这一解释如今已被否定<ref name="mills_139"/>。他称该名称来源于一位“{{le|赫利之子勒德|Lud son of Heli|勒德王}}”（King Lud），此人据传占领了这一城市，并将其命名为“凯尔勒德”（Kaerlud）<ref name=london_009>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/02/books/chapters/02-1st-ackro.html?ex=1225339200&en=b9c2c11ad6e1f435&ei=5070&pagewanted=3|title=London|last=Ackroyd|first=Peter|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2008-10-28|date=2001-12-02|isbn=978-0-7011-7279-4|archive-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830215944/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/12/02/books/chapters/02-1st-ackro.html?ex=1225339200&en=b9c2c11ad6e1f435&ei=5070&pagewanted=3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

自1898年起，人们普遍认为该名称来源于[[凯尔特人|凯尔特人]]，意为“名为伦蒂诺斯（Londinos）者所有之地”；但这一解释此后亦被推翻<ref name="mills_139"/>。{{le|理查德·科特斯|Richard Coates}}于1998年提出该名称来源于前凯尔特古欧洲语言名称“(p)lowonida”，意为“河流过宽无法涉足”，代指流经伦敦的[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]的一部分；由此这一定居点获得其凯尔特名称“Lowonidonjon”<ref name=coates>{{Cite journal |last=Coates |first=Richard |year=1998 |title=A new explanation of the name of London |journal=Transactions of the Philological Society |volume=96 |issue=2 |pages=203–229 |url=http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/pdf/10.1111/1467-968X.00027 |doi=10.1111/1467-968X.00027 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0UqnAy?url=http://www.blackwell-synergy.com/doi/pdf/10.1111/1467-968X.00027 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes |author= |access-date=2015-05-21 }}</ref>，但距离“伦敦”仍有一定差距。其最大的问题在于拉丁名称“Londinium”和现代威尔士语“Llundain”之间的不同；后者照理应为“(h)lōndinion”（非“londīnion”），来源于先前的“loundiniom”。当然，亦有可能是威尔士名称本身来源于日后的英语名称，因此便无法由这一形式得出其原名。

1889年之前，“伦敦”一名仅為官方用于称呼[[伦敦城|伦敦城]]，但此后亦用于称呼[[伦敦郡|伦敦郡]]及今日的[[大伦敦|大伦敦]]<ref name="mills_140"/>。

===史前===
倫敦附近的斯旺斯孔布（Swanscombe）曾經發現四十萬年前的舊石器時期人類化石。考古界稱為斯旺斯孔布人（Swanscombe Man）。 

最近的两项发现表明在泰晤士河伦敦地区非常早便有人定居。1999年，一座[[青铜时代|青铜时代]]桥梁的遗迹在[[沃克斯霍尔桥|沃克斯霍尔桥]]北部河滩上被发现<ref name="Denison">{{cite journal |last=Denison |first=Simon |title=First 'London Bridge' in River Thames at Vauxhall |journal=British Archaeology |date=July 1999 |issue=46 |url=http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba46/ba46news.html |accessdate=2011-04-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0WdLQ0?url=http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba46/ba46news.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这一桥梁可能跨越泰晤士河，亦可能连接一座至今已不存在的河中岛屿。树木学研究可将其木料追溯至公元前1500年<ref name="Denison"/>。2010年，一座大型木质结构的地基在沃克斯霍尔桥南部的泰晤士河河滩上被发现，可追溯至公元前4500年<ref name="Milne">{{cite web |last=Milne |first=Gustav |title=London's Oldest Foreshore Structure! |url=http://www.thamesdiscovery.org/frog-blog/london-s-oldest-find-discovered-at-vauxhall |work=Frog Blog |publisher=Thames Discovery Programme |accessdate=2011-04-15 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0WtZpl?url=http://www.thamesdiscovery.org/frog-blog/london-s-oldest-find-discovered-at-vauxhall |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这一中石器时代结构的功能至今尚不明确。两个建筑都位于南岸的一个天然跨河点，在此{{le|埃夫拉河|River Effra}}注入泰晤士河<ref name="Milne"/>。

===罗马伦敦===
[[File:Map_of_London,_1300.svg|thumb]]的范围仍然局限于其[[伦敦城墙|罗马城墙]]之内。]]

虽然这一区域内仍然有[[布立吞人_(凯尔特)|布立吞人]]定居的痕迹，最初的主要定居点仍然是由[[罗马帝国|罗马人]]在公元43年入侵之后建立的<ref name="roman">{{Cite book |title=Roman London |last=Perring |first=Dominic |year=1991 |publisher=Routledge |location=London |isbn=978-0-203-23133-3|page=1 |ref=harv }}</ref>。这一定居点只维持到公元61年，[[布狄卡|布狄卡]]率领[[爱西尼|爱西尼]]部落将之攻陷并焚毁<ref name=london_010>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/timeline/romanbritain_timeline_noflash.shtml |title=British History Timeline —Roman Britain |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-06-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0V1GXn?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/timeline/romanbritain_timeline_noflash.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此后精心规划并得到重建的伦蒂尼恩获得了繁荣，并于100年取代[[科尔切斯特|科尔切斯特]]成为罗马行省[[不列颠尼亚_(罗马行省)|不列颠尼亚]]的首府。在2世纪这一城市发展达到顶峰，人口达近60,000人。

===盎格鲁-撒克逊伦敦（及维京时期）===
5世纪初罗马统治崩溃，伦敦不再为首府，伦蒂尼恩城也几乎被遗弃，虽然罗马文明在今[[圣马田教堂|圣马田教堂]]附近地区持续存在直至约450年<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Past/MissingLink/Themes/TML_themes_Londinium.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090108092449/http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Past/MissingLink/Themes/TML_themes_Londinium.htm |archivedate=2009-01-08 |publisher=Museum of London |title=The last days of Londinium |accessdate=2013-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。自约500起，[[盎格鲁-撒克逊人|盎格鲁-撒克逊人]]的定居点{{le|盎格鲁-撒克逊伦敦|Anglo-Saxon London|伦敦维克}}（Lundenwic）在古罗马城市西侧发展起来<ref name=london_011>{{cite web |url=http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Past/MissingLink/Themes/TML_themes_Lundenwic.htm |title=The early years of Lundenwic |publisher=The [[Museum_of_London|Museum of London]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080610043903/http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Past/MissingLink/Themes/TML_themes_Lundenwic.htm |archivedate=2008-06-10 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref>。至680年，该城已复苏至成为一个主要港口，但仍然没有大规模生产产品的证据存在。自820年代起，由于[[维京人|维京人]]频繁入侵，该城开始衰退。历史上总共记载了三次维京人对伦敦的入侵；851年和886年他们两次成功，而在994年则失败<ref name="Viking Attacks">{{cite web|url=https://web.cn.edu/kwheeler/viking_attacklist.html?showall=1|title=Viking Attacks|publisher=https://web.cn.edu/kwheeler/|accessdate=2014-08-24|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101055729/https://web.cn.edu/kwheeler/viking_attacklist.html?showall=1|archive-date=2016-01-01}}</ref>。

维京人在英格兰东部和北部大片地区建立起丹麦律法统治的[[丹麥區|丹麥區]]（Danelaw），统治范围由伦敦一直持续至[[切斯特|切斯特]]。这一地区在政治和地理上的维京统治由丹麦国王{{le|古瑟伦|Guthrum}}和西撒克逊国王[[阿尔弗雷德大帝|阿尔弗雷德大帝]]于886年协定认可。丹麦律法统治在此后数个世纪内继续延续。根据《[[盎格鲁-撒克逊编年史|盎格鲁-撒克逊编年史]]》的记载，阿尔弗雷德大帝于886年“重建”伦敦。考古研究表明伦敦维克在此时废弃，社会生活和贸易在古罗马城墙内重新发展起来。此后伦敦缓慢发展，而在950年之后则得到巨大的发展<ref name="blackwell">{{cite encyclopedia |last=Vince|first= Alan|year=2001|title=London|editors= Lapidge, Michael; Blair, John; Keynes, Simon; Scragg, Donald |encyclopedia=The Blackwell Encyclopedia of Anglo-Saxon England |publisher= Blackwell |isbn=978-0-631-22492-1}}</ref>。

至11世纪，伦敦已是全英格兰最大的城镇。国王[[忏悔者爱德华|忏悔者爱德华]]以[[罗曼式建筑|罗曼式风格]]重建[[威斯敏斯特教堂|威斯敏斯特教堂]]，这亦是全欧洲最为宏伟的教堂之一。盎格鲁-撒克逊英格兰先前的首都为[[温切斯特|温切斯特]]，而此时伦敦则成为外国贸易者的主要活动地点以及战争期间的主要据点。在[[弗兰克·梅利·斯坦顿|弗兰克·斯坦顿]]看来，伦敦“有其资源，并在其尊严和政治自我觉悟方面快速发展，作为首都十分恰当<ref>{{cite book|authorlink=Frank Stenton|last=Stenton|first= Frank|year=1971|title=Anglo-Saxon England|pages=538–539|publisher= Oxford University Press|edition=3rd|isbn=978-0-19-280139-5}}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia |last=Blair |first= John |year=2001|title=Westminster|editors= Lapidge, Michael; Blair, John; Keynes, Simon; Scragg, Donald |encyclopedia=The Blackwell Encyclopedia of Anglo-Saxon England|publisher= Blackwell |isbn=978-0-631-22492-1}}</ref>。”

===中世纪===
[[File:Westminster_Abbey_by_Canaletto,_1749.jpg|thumb]]（加纳莱托，1749年作）为[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]，亦是伦敦最古老和最为重要的建筑之一。]]
[[威廉一世_(英格兰)|诺曼底公爵威廉]]在[[黑斯廷斯战役|黑斯廷斯战役]]中获胜，并于1066年圣诞节于落成的威斯敏斯特教堂加冕为[[英格兰君主列表|英格兰国王]]<ref name=london_015>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/normans/1066_06.shtml |title=History – 1066 – King William |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-05-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0Yen4R?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/normans/1066_06.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。威廉于城东南角建造[[伦敦塔|伦敦塔]]，用于震慑当地居民，这也是第一座在英格兰以石料重建的诺曼城堡<ref name=london_016>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/architecture_02.shtml |title=A History of British Architecture — White Tower |last=Tinniswood |first=Adrian |authorlink=Adrian Tinniswood |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-05-05 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0ZWxtH?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/architecture_02.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。1097年，[[威廉二世_(英格兰)|威廉二世]]开始在[[威斯敏斯特教堂|威斯敏斯特教堂]]附近兴建[[威斯敏斯特宫|威斯敏斯特厅]]。这一建筑成为之后威斯敏斯特宫的基础<ref name=london_017>{{cite web |url=http://www.parliament.uk/about/history/building.cfm |title=UK Parliament — Parliament: The building |date=2007-11-09 |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=2008-04-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080311032051/http://www.parliament.uk/about/history/building.cfm |archivedate=2008-03-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=london_018>{{cite web |url=http://www.parliament.uk/parliament/guide/palace.htm |title=Palace of Westminster |publisher=UK Parliament |accessdate=2008-04-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080404171249/http://www.parliament.uk/parliament/guide/palace.htm |archivedate=2008-04-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

英格兰的中央政府机构此前一直伴随宫廷在全国活动，而到了12世纪这些机构逐渐发展庞大并变得复杂，由此开始固定于一地进行运作。多数时候这一地点为威斯敏斯特，而由温切斯特迁来的国库则位于伦敦塔。[[威斯敏斯特|威斯敏斯特市]]在行政层面成为一个真正的首都，而临近的伦敦城则仍旧是英国最大城市及商业中心，并在其[[伦敦市法团|伦敦市法团]]体系管理之下得到繁荣。1100年，此地人口大约为18,000；至1300年人口则增长到近100,000<ref name=london_019>{{Cite book|last=Schofield|first=John|last2=Vince|first2=Alan|author2-link=Alan Vince|title=Medieval Towns: The Archaeology of British Towns in Their European Setting|publisher=Continuum International Publishing Group|year=2003|isbn=978-0-8264-6002-8|url=http://books.google.com/?id=Qu7QLC7g7VgC&pg=PA26&lpg=PA26&dq=london+population+1100+-+1300|page=26|ref=harv}}</ref>。

14世纪中叶[[黑死病|黑死病]]入侵，伦敦失去其近三分之一的人口<ref>{{Cite journal |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/middle_ages/black_01.shtml |title=Black Death |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0ZmE6P?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/middle_ages/black_01.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no |publisher=BBC History |accessdate=2008-11-03 |ref=harv |journal= }}</ref>。1381年，伦敦成为[[瓦特·泰勒农民起义|瓦特·泰勒农民起义]]的中心<ref name=london_020>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/richard_ii_king.shtml |title=Richard II (1367–1400) |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-10-12 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0aYnXz?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/historic_figures/richard_ii_king.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===16世紀至18世紀===
[[File:London_-_John_Norden's_map_of_1593.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Great_Fire_London.jpg|thumb]]摧毁该城的许多地区。]]
[[都铎时期|都铎时期]][[英格兰宗教改革|宗教改革]]逐渐推动向新教的过渡，伦敦的许多区域也由教会所有转向私人所有<ref name=pevsner>[[Nikolaus_Pevsner|Pevsner, Nikolaus]]. ''London I: The Cities of London and Westminster'' rev. edition, 1962. Introduction p. 48.</ref>。未染色和未修整的羊毛制品由伦敦出口至[[低地国家|低地国家]]沿岸；这些产品在这一地区被认为不可或缺<ref>J. G. Pounds (1976). "An Historical Geography of Europe 450 B.C.-A.D. 1330, Part 1330". p. 430. CUP Archive,</ref>。但此时英国的海上贸易基本难出欧洲西北部海域。通往[[意大利|意大利]]及[[地中海|地中海]]的商路通常经过[[安特卫普|安特卫普]]并跨越[[阿尔卑斯山|阿尔卑斯山]]，而任何经由[[直布罗陀海峡|直布罗陀海峡]]前往或发自英格兰的船只一般都属意大利或[[杜布罗夫尼克|拉古萨]]。1565年1月[[荷兰|尼德兰]]重新对英格兰船运开放，商业立刻得到重大的发展<ref>Ramsay, George Daniel (1986). The Queen's Merchants and the Revolt of the Netherlands: The End of the Antwerp Mart. Volume 2, pp. 1 and 62–63. Manchester University Press. ISBN 978-0-7190-1849-7</ref>。[[皇家交易所_(伦敦)|皇家交易所]]在这一时期建立起来<ref>The life and times of Sir Thomas Gresham, founder of the Royal Exchange: including notices of many of his contemporaries. With illustrations, Volume 2, pages 80–81, John William Burgon, E. Wilson, 1839.</ref>。[[重商主义|重商主义]]得到发展，诸如[[不列颠东印度公司|东印度公司]]这样的垄断贸易企业也建立起来，将贸易范围扩展至[[新大陆|新大陆]]。伦敦成为[[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]的首要港口，大量移民从英格兰和海外迁入，其人口由1530年的约50,000增长至1605年的约225,000<ref name=pevsner/>。

16世纪时，[[威廉·莎士比亚|威廉·莎士比亚]]和其他剧作家生活在伦敦。至1603年都铎时期结束，伦敦仍是一座颇为紧密简洁的城市。1605年11月5日，[[火药阴谋|火药阴谋]]策划者试图在威斯敏斯特刺杀[[詹姆斯六世及一世|詹姆斯一世]]<ref name=london_023>{{Cite book |title=James I |url=https://archive.org/details/jamesi0000durs |last=Durston |first=Christopher|year=1993 |publisher=Routledge |location=London |isbn=978-0-415-07779-8 |page=[https://archive.org/details/jamesi0000durs/page/59 59] |ref=harv }}</ref>。17世纪初，伦敦开始受到[[腺鼠疫|鼠疫]]的侵袭<ref name=london_024>{{cite web |url=http://urbanrim.org.uk/plague%20list.htm |title=A List of National Epidemics of Plague in England 1348–1665 |publisher=Urban Rim |date=2009-12-04 |accessdate=2010-05-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5gVUqcycW?url=http://urbanrim.org.uk/plague%20list.htm |archivedate=2009-05-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，1665年至1666年的[[伦敦大瘟疫|大瘟疫]]导致近100,000人死亡，占到伦敦人口的五分之一<ref name=london_025>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/plague/story.html |title=Story of the plague |publisher=Channel 4 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0bPVKk?url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/plague/story.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref>。

1666年[[伦敦大火|伦敦大火]]由布丁巷发起，并迅速横扫全城的木质建筑<ref name="Samuel Pepys' Diary">{{Cite book |last=Pepys |first=Samuel |authorlink=Samuel Pepys |title=The Diary of Samuel Pepys |volume=45: August/September 1666 |date=1666-09-02 |origyear=1893 |editor=[[Mynors_Bright|Mynors Bright]] (decipherer) |editor2=[[Henry_B._Wheatley|Henry B. Wheatley]] |url=http://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/4167/pg4167.html |ref=harv |isbn=978-0-520-22167-3 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0bzHYi?url=http://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/4167/pg4167.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no |access-date=2015-05-21 }}</ref>。重建工作耗时超过十年，由[[罗伯特·胡克|罗伯特·胡克]]主导<ref name=london_026>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/civil_war_revolution/after_fire_02.shtml |title=London After the Great Fire: Civil War and Revolution |author=Schofield, John |date=2011-02-17 |publisher=BBC History |accessdate=2013-07-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0ckJxq?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/civil_war_revolution/after_fire_02.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name=london_027>{{cite web |url=http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Special/LondonsBurning/Themes/1405/ |title=Rebuilding after the fire |publisher=Museum of London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080201204641/http://www.museumoflondon.org.uk/English/EventsExhibitions/Special/LondonsBurning/Themes/1405/ |archivedate=2008-02-01 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref><ref name=london_028>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/?id=jX8ZAAAAIAAJ&q=rebuilding+of+london&dq=rebuilding+of+london|title=The Rebuilding of London After the Great Fire|publisher=Thomas Fiddian|year=1940|accessdate=2008-04-27}}</ref>。1708年[[克里斯多佛·雷恩|克里斯多佛·雷恩]]设计的[[圣保罗座堂|圣保罗座堂]]竣工。[[乔治王时代|乔治王时代]]，新的区域诸如[[五月墟市|五月墟市]]在西部建立起来，而新的泰晤士河桥梁则推动[[南伦敦|南伦敦]]的发展。在东部，[[伦敦港|伦敦港]]向下游扩张。

1762年，[[乔治三世|乔治三世]]购得[[白金汉宫|白金汉宫]]，并在此后75年内对其扩建。18世纪时，伦敦饱受犯罪困扰，1750年{{le|鲍街警探|Bow Street Runners}}（Bow Street Runners）作为一支专业警察队伍成立<ref>"[http://www.pbs.org/kqed/demonbarber/madding/thieftaker.html Thief Taker, Constable, Police] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pbs.org/kqed/demonbarber/madding/thieftaker.html |date=20111012101644 }}". Public Broadcasting Service (PBS).</ref>。超过200项罪名可宣判死刑<ref>{{cite news |last=Jackson |first=Peter |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8181192.stm |title=Rough justice – Victorian style |work=BBC News |date=2009-08-03 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105210454/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8181192.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括偷盗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,894775,00.html |title=National Affairs: Capital punishment: a fading practice |work=Time |location=New York |date=1960-03-21 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011174652/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,894775,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。多数城内出生的儿童在三岁前即死亡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/victorians/foundling_01.shtml |title=The Foundling Hospital |publisher=BBC History |date=2011-02-17 |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-date=2011-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111013092142/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/british/victorians/foundling_01.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[咖啡店|咖啡店]]成为讨论观点的热门场所，[[识字|识字率]]逐渐增长，[[印刷机|印刷技术]]的发展使新闻广为传播。[[弗利特街|弗利特街]]成为英国媒体的中心。

塞缪尔·约翰逊说：

{{quote|任何有文化的人都不会愿意离开伦敦。不，先生，当一个人厌烦伦敦，他便厌烦人生；在伦敦，一切人生所需均应有尽有。|[[塞缪尔·约翰逊|塞缪尔·约翰逊]]，1777年<ref name=london_022>{{cite web |url=http://www.samueljohnson.com/tiredlon.html |title=When a man is tired of London, he is tired of life: Samuel Johnson |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0fwREG?url=http://www.samueljohnson.com/tiredlon.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2015-05-21 }}</ref>}}

===近代至今===
[[File:London_Thames_(1930).jpg|thumb]]
[[File:LondonBombedWWII_full.jpg|thumb]]的伦敦街道]]
1831年至1925年间，伦敦是全球最大的城市<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web |url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/i-m/london4.html |title=London: The greatest city |publisher=Channel 4 |accessdate=2008-10-12 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0g3KOn?url=http://www.channel4.com/history/microsites/H/history/i-m/london4.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。过于密集的人口导致[[霍乱|霍乱]]时常发生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sciencemuseum.org.uk/broughttolife/themes/publichealth/cholera.aspx |title=Hidden extras: cholera comes to Victorian London |publisher=The Science Museum |location=London |accessdate=2011-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213064834/http://www.sciencemuseum.org.uk/broughttolife/themes/publichealth/cholera.aspx |archive-date=2011-12-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，1848年的霍乱导致14,000人丧生，而1866年的霍乱则导致6,000人丧生<ref>{{cite web |author= Brown, Robert W. |url= http://www.uncp.edu/home/rwb/london_19c.html |title= London in the Nineteenth Century |publisher= University of North Carolina at Pembroke |accessdate= 2011-12-13 |deadurl= yes |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20111230164544/http://www.uncp.edu/home/rwb/london_19c.html |archivedate= 2011-12-30 }}</ref>。日渐[[交通堵塞|拥堵的交通]]最终使世界上首个地方城市铁道系统建立起来。{{le|大都會工務委員會|Metropolitan Board of Works}}（首長稱主席）负责监督首都及邻近地区的基础设施扩张；1889年该委员会撤廢，{{le|伦敦郡委员会|London County Council}}（London County Council）由首都周围的郡组织成立，作為行政機構。第一次世界大战期间伦敦受到德国轰炸，而第二次世界大战期间[[纳粹德国空军|纳粹德国空军]]的[[伦敦大轰炸|一系列轰炸]]导致超过30,000名伦敦人死亡，大量房屋和其他建筑被摧毁。战争结束之后，英国尚未从战争中恢复过来，便于旧[[温布利球场_(1923年)|温布利球场]]举办[[1948年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1948年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]。

1951年，{{le|不列颠节|Festival of Britain}}于[[南岸_(伦敦)|南岸]]举办。1952年的[[1952年伦敦烟雾事件|大雾霾]]最终引致《[[1956年空气清净法案|1956年空气清净法案]]》的通过，从而终结臭名昭著的伦敦“豆羹雾”（pea soup fogs）状况的发生。1940年代起，伦敦成为大量移民的目的地，他们大多来自其他[[英联邦|英联邦]]国家，例如[[牙买加|牙买加]]、印度、[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]]和[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]，伦敦也成为全欧洲最为多元化的城市之一。

自1960年代中期起，伦敦成为世界青年文化的中心，例如与[[国王路|国王路]]、[[切尔西_(伦敦)|切尔西]]和[[卡纳比街|卡纳比街]]相关的“{{le|摇摆伦敦|Swinging London}}”（Swinging London）亚文化。其开创性的地位在[[朋克摇滚|朋克摇滚]]年代得到复兴。1965年伦敦的行政边界向外扩张以纳入逐渐发展的城市区域，新的行政機構——{{le|大伦敦委员会|Greater London Council}}成立。在[[北爱尔兰问题|北爱尔兰问题]]年代，伦敦多次受到[[爱尔兰共和军临时派|爱尔兰共和军临时派]]的炸弹攻击。种族不平等问题在{{le|1981年布里克斯顿骚乱|1981 Brixton riot}}中得到突出的体现。

大伦敦的人口在第二次世界大战后的数十年内逐渐下跌，由1939年的近860万下跌至1980年代的680万。伦敦的主要港区向下游的[[菲力斯杜港|费利克斯托]]和{{le|蒂尔伯里港|Port of Tilbury|蒂尔伯里}}迁移，而[[伦敦码头区|伦敦码头区]]则作为[[金丝雀码头|金丝雀码头]]得到重新的开发。这一切都起源于1980年代伦敦逐渐向全球金融中心角色的转变。

1980年代[[泰晤士河防洪闸|泰晤士河防洪闸]]落成，以保护伦敦免受[[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]大潮的侵袭。1986年{{Link-en|大伦敦委员会|Greater London Council}}废除，伦敦也成为全球唯一没有中央行政机构的大都市。2000年，[[大伦敦政府|大伦敦政府]]建立，伦敦重新得到全城范围的行政管理。为庆祝21世纪的到来，[[千禧巨蛋|千禧巨蛋]]、[[伦敦眼|伦敦眼]]和[[千禧桥|千禧桥]]兴建起来。2005年7月6日，伦敦获得[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会]]举办权，由此也成为首座三次举办[[奥林匹克运动会|奥林匹克运动会]]的城市<ref>{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/front_page/4655555.stm |title= London beats Paris to 2012 Games |publisher= BBC Sport |date= 2005-07-06 |accessdate= 2012-09-28 |archive-date= 2007-02-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070213094506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/front_page/4655555.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2015年2月，大伦敦的总人口估计为860万，达到自1939年来的最高点<ref>{{Cite web|title = London's population hits 8.6m record high|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-31082941|website = BBC News|accessdate = 2015-05-21|archive-date = 2020-12-01|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201201211559/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-london-31082941|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==政府==

===地方政府===
{{Main|伦敦地方政府|伦敦地方政府历史|伦敦政府首长列表}}
伦敦的行政管理分为两个级别——全市范围的战略性级别和地方级别。全市范围的行政由[[大伦敦政府|大伦敦政府]]进行协调，而地方行政则由33个较小的政府执行<ref name=london_032>{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/gla/ |title=About the Greater London Authority |publisher=London Government |accessdate=2008-09-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0hYGdz?url=http://www.london.gov.uk/gla/ |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大伦敦政府包括两个选举产生的机构：[[伦敦市长_(大伦敦)|伦敦市长]]，拥有行政权力；[[伦敦议会|伦敦议会]]（London Assembly），负责监督市长的决策并有权批准或否决每年市长的预算提案。
大伦敦政府的总部位于[[萨瑟克|萨瑟克]]的[[倫敦市政廳_(南華克)|市政厅]]，伦敦市长为[[萨迪克·汗|萨迪克·汗]]。市长的法定规划方案称《[[伦敦规划|伦敦规划]]》（London Plan），最新的一份伦敦计划于2016年3月制定，2017年1月出版<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.london.gov.uk/what-we-do/planning/london-plan/current-london-plan |title=The current London Plan |website=London Assembly |date=January 2017 |author=Mayor of London |accessdate=2017-04-22 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210230903/https://www.london.gov.uk/what-we-do/planning/london-plan/current-london-plan |dead-url=no }} [https://www.london.gov.uk/sites/default/files/the_london_plan_2016_jan_2017_fix.pdf PDF] {{Wayback|url=https://www.london.gov.uk/sites/default/files/the_london_plan_2016_jan_2017_fix.pdf |date=20170423062539 }}</ref>。伦敦的地方政府为32个[[伦敦自治市|伦敦自治市]]的议会以及[[伦敦市法团|伦敦市法团]]（City of London Corporation）<ref name=london_035>{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/london/links.jsp |title=Links to other websites — London boroughs |publisher=London Government |accessdate=2008-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071019055428/http://www.london.gov.uk/london/links.jsp |archivedate=2007-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，负责大多数地方服务機構，例如地方规划、学校、[[社会工作|社会服务]]、地方道路和垃圾收集。诸如{{le|伦敦废品处理机构|Waste disposal authorities in London|废品处理}}这类的功能则时常联合执行。2009年–2010年，伦敦各地方政府及大伦敦政府的总支出略多于£220亿（地方政府：£147亿；大伦敦政府：£74亿）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.communities.gov.uk/documents/statistics/pdf/1911067.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-21 |archive-date=2012-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114050414/http://www.communities.gov.uk/documents/statistics/pdf/1911067.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

大伦敦的执法机构（除[[伦敦城|伦敦城]]外）为[[伦敦警察厅|伦敦警察厅]]，由市长通过{{le|市长警务和犯罪问题办公室|Mayor's Office for Policing and Crime}}（Mayor's Office for Policing and Crime；MOPAC）进行监督<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/priorities/policing-crime/about-mopac |title=About MOPAC |publisher=Greater London Authority |accessdate=2013-05-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130411075040/http://www.london.gov.uk/priorities/policing-crime/about-mopac |archivedate=2013-04-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://policeauthority.org/Metropolitan/ |title= MPA: Metropolitan Police Authority |publisher= Metropolitan Police Authority |date= 2012-05-22 |accessdate= 2013-05-04 |archive-date= 2020-09-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132310/http://policeauthority.org/Metropolitan/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。伦敦城拥有自己的警隊，即[[伦敦市警察|伦敦市警察]]<ref name="Policing">{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/gla/policing.jsp |title=Policing |publisher=Greater London Authority |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121173357/http://www.london.gov.uk/gla/policing.jsp |archivedate=2008-01-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{le|英国交通警察|British Transport Police}}（British Transport Police）负责为[[英国全国铁路|全国铁路]]和[[伦敦地铁|伦敦地铁]]提供警务<ref name="BTP">{{cite web |url=http://www.btp.police.uk/about_us/areas.aspx |title=Areas |publisher=British Transport Police |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0hdc31?url=http://www.btp.police.uk/about_us/areas.aspx |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

大伦敦的[[法规|法定]][[英國消防機構|消防和救援機構]]由[[伦敦消防队|伦敦消防队]]（London Fire Brigade）提供。伦敦消防队由{{le|伦敦消防和应急计划局|London Fire and Emergency Planning Authority}}（London Fire and Emergency Planning Authority）组织，是世界上第三大消防部門<ref name="LFB">{{cite web |url=http://www.london-fire.gov.uk/WhoWeAre.asp |title=Who we are |publisher=London Fire Brigade |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0hzveR?url=http://www.london-fire.gov.uk/WhoWeAre.asp |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[国民保健署_(英国)|国民保健署]]的[[紧急医疗服务|救护服务]]由{{le|倫敦救護站|London Ambulance Service|国民保健署信托伦敦救护站}}（London Ambulance Service NHS Trust）提供，这是全世界最大的免费紧急救护服务機構<ref name="LAS">{{cite web |url=http://www.londonambulance.nhs.uk/about_us.aspx |title=About us |publisher=London Ambulance Service NHS Trust |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0iCW89?url=http://www.londonambulance.nhs.uk/about_us.aspx |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{le|伦敦空中救护|London Air Ambulance}}（London Air Ambulance）在需要时会与伦敦救护站协同行动。{{le|女王陛下海岸警卫队|Her Majesty's Coastguard}}（Her Majesty's Coastguard）和[[皇家全国救生艇协会|皇家全国救生艇协会]]在[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]上运营<ref name="Coastguard">{{cite web |url=http://www.mcga.gov.uk/c4mca/mcga07-home/aboutus/mcga-online/mcga-sailing-cg66/dops_-_all-cg66-stationlist.htm |title=Station list |year=2007 |publisher=Maritime and Coastguard Agency |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0jzXE7?url=http://www.mcga.gov.uk/c4mca/mcga07-home/aboutus/mcga-online/mcga-sailing-cg66/dops_-_all-cg66-stationlist.htm |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Lifeboat">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/1739401.stm |title=Thames lifeboat service launched |date=2002-01-02 |work=BBC News |accessdate=2009-08-25 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0kXnz9?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/1739401.stm |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，由{{le|伦敦港务局|Port of London Authority}}（Port of London Authority）管辖，覆盖范围由{{le|特丁顿船闸|Teddington Lock}}一直延续至北海<ref name="portlondonauthority">{{cite web |url=http://www.pla.co.uk/assets/Port_of_London_Act_1968__revised_.pdf |title=Port of London Act 1968 |accessdate=2013-11-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203005959/http://www.pla.co.uk/assets/Port_of_London_Act_1968__revised_.pdf |archivedate=2013-12-03 }}</ref>。

===国家政府===
伦敦为[[英国政府|英国政府]]所在地。许多政府机构都临近[[威斯敏斯特宫|威斯敏斯特宫]]，尤其是[[白厅|白厅]]一带，包括[[英国首相|英国首相]]官邸[[唐宁街10号|唐宁街10号]]<ref name=london_036>{{cite web |url=http://www.number10.gov.uk/output/Page1.asp |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080510193022/http://www.number10.gov.uk/output/Page1.asp |archivedate=2008-05-10 |title=10 Downing Street — Official Website |accessdate=2008-04-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。英国国会常稱“国会之母”（这一名称原先由{{le|约翰·布莱特|John Bright}}用于称呼英格兰）<ref name="london_037">{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/talking_politics/96021.stm |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-06-06 |date=1998-06-03 |title=UK Politics: Talking Politics — The 'Mother of Parliaments' |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0l5vww?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/talking_politics/96021.stm |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，为其他国家的[[议会制|议会制度]]提供借鉴<ref name="london_037"/>。伦敦的国会议员共有73人，由各自的{{le|伦敦国会选区列表|List of Parliamentary constituencies in London|选区}}选出，在[[英国下议院|英国下议院]]任职。截至2015年5月，45名议员来自[[工党_(英国)|工党]]，27名议员来自[[保守党_(英国)|保守党]]，1名议员来自[[自由民主党_(英国)|自由民主党]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = General Election Results 2015|url = http://data.london.gov.uk/dataset/general-election-results-2015|website = London DataStore|accessdate = 2015-05-10|publisher = [[Greater_London_Authority|Greater London Authority]]|date = 2015-05-08|archive-date = 2016-05-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160504063550/http://data.london.gov.uk/dataset/general-election-results-2015|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==地理==
{{Main|伦敦地理}}

===范围===
[[File:London,_United_Kingdom.JPG|thumb]]
[[大伦敦|大伦敦]]为覆盖伦敦全区的顶级行政单位<ref group="注">大伦敦并非传统意义上的“城市”，即由君主授予其[[英国城市地位|城市地位]]。</ref>。规模较小的[[伦敦城|伦敦城]]为伦敦的核心，历史悠久，曾经囊括整个伦敦，但此后市区开始扩张，[[伦敦市法团|伦敦市法团]]拒绝与郊区合并，导致“伦敦”一词有许多不同的定义<ref name="chancery">{{Cite journal|last=Beavan|first=Charles|coauthors=Bickersteth, Harry|title=Reports of Cases in Chancery, Argued and Determined in the Rolls Court|publisher=Saunders and Benning|year=1865|url=http://books.google.com/?id=YFYDAAAAQAAJ|ref=harv}}</ref>。大伦敦近百分之四十的地区属于{{le|伦敦邮区|London postal district}}，“LONDON”一词為其[[郵鎮|郵鎮]]名<ref name=london_042>{{Cite book|last=Stationery Office|title=The Inner London Letter Post|publisher=H.M.S.O|year=1980|isbn=978-0-10-251580-0|page=128|ref=harv}}</ref><ref name=map_post>{{Cite book|title=London Postcode and Administrative Boundaries|publisher=Geographers' A-Z Map Company|author=Geographers' A-Z Map Company|year=2008|edition=6|isbn=978-1-84348-592-6|ref=harv}}</ref>。

伦敦电话[[电话号码分类计划|区号]]（020）覆盖地区广大，面积大致与大伦敦相近，但有一些较远的大伦敦区域在其范围之外，而有一些大伦敦之外的区域则在其范围之内。大伦敦的边界在一些地区{{le|大伦敦边界变更历史|List of Greater London boundary changes|与M25高速公路相符}}<ref name=london_044>{{cite web |url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/SI/si1993/Uksi_19930441_en_1.htm |title=The Essex, Greater London and Hertfordshire (County and London Borough Boundaries) Order |year=1993 |publisher=Office of Public Sector Information |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0lyLLA?url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/SI/si1993/Uksi_19930441_en_1.htm |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

市区的进一步扩张如今已经受到[[伦敦绿带圈|伦敦绿带圈]]的限制<ref name=london_040>{{Cite book|last=Dilys|first=M Hill|title=Urban Policy and Politics in Britain|publisher=St. Martin's Press|year=2000|isbn=978-0-312-22745-6|page=268|ref=harv}}</ref>，但其都会区有时可以延伸至其界限之外，由此便有[[大伦敦都会区|大伦敦都会区]]这一概念。在这一区域之外则是宽广的[[伦敦通勤带|伦敦通勤带]]<ref name=london_041>{{cite web |url=http://www.london.gov.uk/assembly/reports/plansd/london_regional_200104.pdf |title=London in its Regional Setting |publisher=London Assembly |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527193714/http://www.london.gov.uk/assembly/reports/plansd/london_regional_200104.pdf |archivedate=2008-05-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大伦敦有时划分为[[内伦敦|内伦敦]]和[[外伦敦|外伦敦]]<ref name=london_045>{{cite book |url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/RevisedStatutes/Acts/ukpga/1963/cukpga_19630033_en_1 |title=London Government Act 1963 |publisher=Office of Public Sector Information |accessdate=2008-05-06 |isbn=978-0-16-053895-7 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0mVCtM?url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/RevisedStatutes/Acts/ukpga/1963/cukpga_19630033_en_1 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。泰晤士河将伦敦分隔为[[北伦敦|北伦敦]]和[[南伦敦|南伦敦]]，而在其中心则是非正式的[[中伦敦|中伦敦]]。传统上认为伦敦的名义中心是位于原{{le|埃莉诺十字|Eleanor Cross}}的所在地，位于[[特拉法加广场|特拉法加广场]]与[[白厅|白厅]]交汇处附近的[[查令十字|查令十字]]，经纬度大致为{{Coord|51|30|26|N|00|07|39|W|type:city(7,000,000)_region:GB}}.<ref name=london_039>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/london/content/articles/2005/08/15/charingcross_feature.shtml |title=London — Features — Where is the Centre of London? |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5msV6aAO0?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/london/content/articles/2005/08/15/charingcross_feature.shtml |archivedate=2010-01-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===地位===
在伦敦内，[[伦敦城|伦敦城]]和[[西敏市|威斯敏斯特市]]具有[[英国城市地位|城市地位]]，同时伦敦城和大伦敦的剩余地区都为[[英格兰的名誉郡|名誉郡]]<ref name=london_049>{{cite web |url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/acts/acts1997/ukpga_19970023_en_1 |title=Lieutenancies Act 1997 |publisher=OPSI |accessdate=2008-06-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0mpHnm?url=http://www.opsi.gov.uk/acts/acts1997/ukpga_19970023_en_1 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[英格兰的都会郡和非都会郡#大伦敦|大伦敦]]如今囊括过去属于[[米德塞克斯|米德塞克斯]]、[[肯特郡|肯特]]、[[萨里郡|萨里]]、[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯]]及[[赫特福德郡|赫特福德]]{{le|英格兰的历史郡|Historic counties of England|历史郡}}的一些地区<ref name=london_050>{{Cite book|last=Barlow|first=I. M. |title=Metropolitan Government|year=1991|publisher=Routledge|page=346|ref=harv}}</ref>。伦敦作为英格兰及后来英国首都的地位从未得到[[法规|法令]]或其他书面形式上的正式确认{{refn|根据《柯林斯英语词典》对“政府所在地”（the seat of government）的定义<ref name=london_061>(1994) ''Collins English Dictionary'', Collins Education plc.</ref>，由于英格兰没有自己的政府，因此伦敦不是英格兰的首都。根据《牛津英文参考词典》对“最重要城镇”（the most important town）的定义<ref name=london_062>''Oxford English Reference Dictionary'', Oxford English.</ref>和其他机构的定义<ref name=london_063>"HC 501 0304.PDF" (PDF). Parliament Publications</ref>则是如此。|group=注}}

伦敦的地位是根据{{le|宪法惯例|Constitutional convention (political custom)}}形成的，由此使其成为不成文[[英国宪法|英国宪法]]之下的实际首都。英格兰的首都原位于[[温彻斯特|温彻斯特]]，而在12世纪和13世纪[[威斯敏斯特宫|威斯敏斯特宫]]逐渐发展成为[[朝廷|宫廷]]的永久所在地，由此首都也迁移至伦敦，使之成为全国的政治首都<ref name=london_060>{{Cite journal |last=Schofield |first=John |date=June 1999 |title=British Archaeology |publisher=British Archaeology |issue=45 |issn=1357-4442 |url=http://www.britarch.ac.uk/BA/ba45/ba45regs.html |accessdate=2008-05-06 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0mw1Sn?url=http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba45/ba45regs.html |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no |journal= }}</ref>。近年大伦敦亦定义为一个[[區域_(英格蘭)|英格蘭大区]]，在这一语境之下亦可直称为“伦敦”<ref name=region/>。

===地形===
[[File:London_from_Primrose_Hill_May_2013.jpg|thumb]]眺望伦敦]]
[[File:London_in_snow_2_February_2009_387.jpg|thumb]]]]
大伦敦位于[[倫敦盆地|倫敦盆地]]中，总面积为{{convert|1583|km2|sqmi}}，2001年的人口为7,172,036，人口密度为{{convert|4542|PD/km2|PD/sqmi}}。伦敦都会区的总面积为{{convert|8382|km2|sqmi}}，人口为13,709,000，人口密度为{{convert|1510|PD/km2|PD/sqmi}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dgcl.interieur.gouv.fr/sections/a_votre_service/lu_pour_vous/les_grandes_metropol/downloadFile/attachedFile/metropolislondres.pdf?nocache=1254397828.63 |title=Metropolis: 027 London, World Association of the Major Metropolises |accessdate=2010-05-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427084411/http://www.dgcl.interieur.gouv.fr/sections/a_votre_service/lu_pour_vous/les_grandes_metropol/downloadFile/attachedFile/metropolislondres.pdf?nocache=1254397828.63 |archivedate=2011-04-27 }}</ref>。现代的伦敦位于其最主要地理景观——[[泰晤士河|泰晤士河]]兩側，该河流适航度高，由西南至东横贯全城。{{le|泰晤士河河谷|Thames Valley}}为[[河漫滩|河漫滩平原]]，为{{le|国会山 (伦敦)|Parliament Hill, London|国会山}}、{{le|阿丁顿山|Addington Hills}}和[[樱草花山|樱草花山]]等一系列山丘所环绕。泰晤士河过去更为宽广且水浅，[[河流湿地|河流湿地]]遍布期间，高潮期间河岸宽度比今日高出近四倍<ref name=london_065>{{cite book |url= http://books.google.com/?id=M9qvtYYhRtAC&pg=PR11&dq=thames+%22iron+age%22+london+wide+geography+shallow+marsh |title=London: A History |first=Francis|last= Sheppard | page=10 |publisher= Oxford University Press |year=2000 |isbn=978-0-19-285369-1 |accessdate=2008-06-06}}</ref>。

自[[维多利亚时代|维多利亚时代]]起泰晤士河河岸便开始兴建{{le|泰晤士河河岸堤坝|Thames Embankment|河岸堤坝}}，许多位于伦敦的{{le|泰晤士河支流|Tributaries of the River Thames|支流}}今日已流往{{le|伦敦地下河流|Subterranean rivers of London|地下}}。泰晤士河为潮汐河，导致伦敦易受洪水侵袭<ref name=london_066>{{cite web |url=http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/yourenv/eff/1190084/natural_forces/flooding/?version=1&lang=_e |title=Flooding |publisher=UK [[Environment_Agency|Environment Agency]] |accessdate=2006-06-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060215080725/http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/yourenv/eff/1190084/natural_forces/flooding/?version=1&lang=_e |archivedate=2006-02-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。由于{{le|后冰期回弹|Post-glacial rebound}}效应，英国开始缓慢“倾斜”（北高南低），导致[[潮汐|最高水位]]缓慢但持续上升，洪灾威胁逐渐变大<ref name=london_067>{{cite web |url=http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/yourenv/eff/1190084/natural_forces/sealevels/?version=1&lang=_e |title="Sea Levels" – UK Environment Agency |publisher=[[Environment_Agency|Environment Agency]] |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523225152/http://www.environment-agency.gov.uk/yourenv/eff/1190084/natural_forces/sealevels/?version=1&lang=_e |archivedate=2008-05-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

1974年，为抵御这一威胁，耗时近十年的[[泰晤士河防洪闸|泰晤士河防洪闸]]工程开始兴建，于[[伍利奇|伍利奇]]横跨泰晤士河。该防洪闸预计能够持续使用至2070年，但未来的扩建或重建工程现已在讨论之中<ref>{{cite news |first=David |last=Adam |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2009/mar/31/thames-flood-barrier-london |title=Thames Barrier gets extra time as London's main flood defence |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2009-03-31 |accessdate=2009-11-07 |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0n91QT?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2009/mar/31/thames-flood-barrier-london |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

===气候===
{{main|倫敦氣候}}
与全英国南部相似，伦敦为温和的[[海洋性气候|海洋性气候]]（[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]：Cfb）。虽有多雨之名，伦敦本身的年降雨量（{{convert|601|mm|0|abbr=on}}）却要小于[[罗马|罗马]]、[[波尔多|波尔多]]、[[图卢兹|图卢兹]]、[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]甚至[[悉尼|悉尼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/averages/tables/cw_066062_All.shtml|title=Climate statistics for Australian locations|work=bom.gov.au|accessdate=2015-05-22|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015135126/http://www.bom.gov.au/climate/averages/tables/cw_066062_All.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldweather.org/176/c00604.htm |title=Weather Information for Naples |publisher=Worldweather.org |date=2006-10-05 |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2012-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105145214/http://www.worldweather.org/176/c00604.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.meteoam.it/modules.php?name=viewClinoFile&station=289&name_station=Napoli%20CapodichinoVisualizzazione tabella CLINO della stazione / CLINO Averages Listed for the station Napoli Capodichino]{{dead link|date=May 2013}}</ref><ref>[http://www.theweathernetwork.com/ The Weather Network] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theweathernetwork.com/ |date=20170711210930 }} 18 November 2011</ref><ref>[http://france.meteofrance.com/france/climat_france?CLIMAT_PORTLET.path=climatstationn%2F31069001 Prévisions météo de Météo-France – Climat en France] {{Webarchive|url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160517203416/http://france.meteofrance.com/france/climat_france?CLIMAT_PORTLET.path=climatstationn%2F31069001 |date=2016-05-17 }} 18 November 2011</ref><ref>[http://www.worldweather.org/062/c01058.htm World Weather Information Service – Toulouse] {{Wayback|url=http://www.worldweather.org/062/c01058.htm |date=20161107131628 }} 18 November 2011</ref>。全伦敦的极端气温高至2003年8月邱园的{{convert|38.1|°C|°F|1}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1256/wea.10.04B/pdf|title=August 2003 weather|accessdate=2012-09-18|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104050856/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1256/wea.10.04B/pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，低至1962年1月诺索尔特的{{convert|-16.1|°C|°F|1}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.personal.dundee.ac.uk/~taharley/british_weather_in_january.htm |title=January 1962 weather |accessdate=2012-09-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150903235843/https://www.personal.dundee.ac.uk/~taharley/british_weather_in_january.htm |archivedate=2015-09-03 }}</ref>。
[[File:Summer_Love_of_Russell_Square.jpg|thumb]]
伦敦夏季通常温暖，时而炎热，七月平均最高温度为{{convert|24|°C|°F|1}}。每年平均有31日最高气温高于{{convert|25|°C|°F|1}}，4.2日最高气温高于{{convert|30.0|°C|°F|1}}。[[2003年欧洲热浪|2003年欧洲热浪]]期间有连续14日最高气温高于{{convert|30|°C|°F|1}}，连续两日气温达{{convert|38|°C|°F|1}}，导致数百人因相关原因丧生<ref>{{cite journal|title=The impact of the 2003 heat wave on daily mortality in England and Wales and the use of rapid weekly mortality estimates|journal=Eurosurveillance|volume=10|issue=7|date=2005-07-01|first1=H|last1=Johnson|first2=RS|last2=Kovats|first3=G|last3=McGregor|first4=J|last4=Stedman|first5=M|last5=Gibbs|first6=H|last6=Walton6|url=http://www.eurosurveillance.org/ViewArticle.aspx?ArticleId=558|access-date=2015-05-22|archive-date=2017-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703142637/http://www.eurosurveillance.org/ViewArticle.aspx?ArticleId=558|dead-url=no}}</ref>。冬季通常湿冷，气温变化较小。降雪时有发生，对交通会产生一定影响。春季和夏季气候相近，较为怡人。作为大城市，伦敦受[[热岛效应|热岛效应]]影响显著<ref>{{cite web |url=http://legacy.london.gov.uk/mayor/environment/climate-change/docs/UHI_summary_report.pdf |title=London's Urban Heat Island: A Summary for Decision Makers |publisher=Greater London Authority |date=October 2006 |accessdate=2015-04-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120816015955/http://legacy.london.gov.uk/mayor/environment/climate-change/docs/UHI_summary_report.pdf |archivedate=2012-08-16 }}</ref>，市中心气温有时比郊区要高出{{convert|5|C-change|0|}}。在下表中，这一效应可由伦敦希思罗机场（伦敦以西15英里）同伦敦气候中心（伦敦中部）的比较中看出<ref>{{cite news|title=Ever warmer as temperatures rival France|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1463994/Ever-warmer-as-temperatures-rival-France.html|publisher=Telegraph|date=2015-05-16|accessdate=2015-05-22|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128082055/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1463994/Ever-warmer-as-temperatures-rival-France.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

