根据[[英国国家统计署|英国国家统计署]]基于[[2011年英国人口普查|2011年人口普查]]的数据估计，伦敦8,173,941名居民中由59.8%为[[白人|白人]]，其中44.9%为[[白种英国人|白种英国人]]，2.2%为{{le|爱尔兰人移民英国|Irish migration to Great Britain|白种爱尔兰人}}，0.1%为[[吉普赛人|吉普赛人]]/{{le|爱尔兰游居者|Irish Travellers}}，12.1%则归类为{{le|其他白种人 (英国族群归类|Other White (classification of ethnicity in the UK)|其他白种人}}。

20.9%的伦敦人为{{le|亚裔英国人|British Asian|亚裔}}或混血亚裔的后代。19.7%为纯亚裔，而混血亚裔则占1.2%。[[印度裔英国人|印度裔]]占总人口的6.6%，[[巴基斯坦裔英國人|巴基斯坦裔]]和[[孟加拉裔英国人|孟加拉裔]]则各占2.7%。[[华裔英国人|华裔]]占1.5%，[[阿拉伯裔英国人|阿拉伯裔]]则占1.3%。其余的4.9%則归类为“其他亚裔”。

伦敦15.6%的人口为[[英國黑人|黑人]]和混血黑人后代。13.3%为纯黑人血统，2.3%则有混血黑人血统。非裔黑人占伦敦人口的7.0%，而{{le|非裔-加勒比英国黑人|British African-Caribbean people|加勒比黑人}}则占4.2%，2.1%则为“其他黑人”。5.0%的人为{{le|混血 (英国族群归类)|Mixed (United Kingdom ethnicity category)|混血族裔}}。

在伦敦的公立学校中，黑人和亚裔的儿童数量同白人儿童的数量比大致是六比四<ref name=london_094>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1564365/One-fifth-of-children-from-ethnic-minorities.html |title=One fifth of children from ethnic minorities |author=Paton, Graeme |date=2007-10-01 |work=The Daily Telegraph |accessdate=2008-06-07 |location=London |ref=harv |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hYR0tUao?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1564365/One-fifth-of-children-from-ethnic-minorities.html |archivedate=2009-06-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。在2011年人口普查中，伦敦0至15岁人口为1,624,768，其中46.4%为白人，19.8为亚裔，19%为黑人，10.8%为混血，4%则为其他族群<ref>{{cite web |author= ONS |url= https://www.nomisweb.co.uk/livelinks/12297.xlsx |title= LC2109EWls - Ethnic group by age |publisher= www.nomisweb.co.uk |accessdate= 2015-03-26 |archive-date= 2020-12-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201210231644/https://www.nomisweb.co.uk/livelinks/12297.xlsx |dead-url= no }}</ref>。2005年1月，一项对伦敦种族和宗教信仰多样性的调查表明在伦敦使用的语言超过300种，人口超过10,000的非本地族群达到50个<ref name=london_090>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2005/jan/21/britishidentity1 |title=Every race, colour, nation and religion on earth |work=The Guardian |location=London |accessdate=2008-05-06 |first=Leo |last=Benedictus |date=2005-01-21 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo0zlxGl?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk/2005/jan/21/britishidentity1 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。英国国家统计署的数据表明，在2010年伦敦出生于国外的人口为2,650,000（33%），相较1997年的1,630,000有显著提升。

2011年人口普查表明大伦敦36.7%的人口生于英国之外<ref name=london_092>{{cite web |url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/census2001/profiles/H-A.asp |title=Census 2001: London |publisher=[[Office_for_National_Statistics|Office for National Statistics]] |accessdate=2006-06-03 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo11Wpqv?url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/census2001/profiles/H-A.asp |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。右表列出2011年普查时伦敦居民最常见的出生国<ref name=Pop2011/>。一部分出生于德国的人口可能为在该国服役的[[英国军队|英国军队]]人员的子女<ref name=london_095>{{cite book |url=http://www.ippr.org.uk/publicationsandreports/publication.asp?id=308 |title=Beyond Black and White: Mapping new immigrant communities |last=Kyambi |first=Sarah |date=2005-09-07 |accessdate=2007-01-20 |isbn=978-1-86030-284-8 |publisher=Institute for Public Policy Research |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo11tc6i?url=http://www.ippr.org.uk/publicationsandreports/publication.asp?id=308 |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。英国国家统计署估计，2009年7月至2010年6月间出生于国外而居住于伦敦的最大五个族群分别生于印度、波兰、爱尔兰、孟加拉国和尼日利亚<ref name=Estimates>{{cite web |url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/downloads/theme_population/population-by-country-of-birth-and-nationality-jul09-jun10.zip |title=Table 1.4: Estimated population resident in the United Kingdom, by foreign country of birth, July 2009 to June 2010 |publisher=Office for National Statistics |accessdate=2011-03-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5yo12D272?url=http://www.statistics.gov.uk/downloads/theme_population/population-by-country-of-birth-and-nationality-jul09-jun10.zip |archivedate=2011-05-19 |deadurl=yes }} Figure given is the central estimate. See the source for 95 per cent [[confidence_interval|confidence interval]]s.</ref>。

===宗教信仰===
{{Main|伦敦宗教}}
{{bar box
|title=伦敦宗教信仰状况（2011年普查）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ons.gov.uk/ons/publications/re-reference-tables.html?edition=tcm%3A77-286262 |title=2011 Census, Key Statistics for Local Authorities in England and Wales |publisher=Ons.gov.uk |date=2012-12-11 |accessdate=2013-05-04 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925200921/http://www.ons.gov.uk/ons/publications/re-reference-tables.html?edition=tcm:77-286262 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
|titlebar=#ddd
|left1=宗教信仰
|right1=百分比(%)
|float=left
|bars=
{{bar percent|[[基督教|基督教]]|purple|48.4}}
{{bar percent|[[无宗教|无宗教信仰]]|violet|20.7}}
{{bar percent|[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]|Green|12.4}}
{{bar percent|未声明|black|8.5}}
{{bar percent|[[印度教|印度教]]|Orange|5.0}}
{{bar percent|[[犹太教|犹太教]]|Blue|1.8}}
